   the btype==1 and btype==2 paths build a local ZopfliLZ77Store, fill it via a
   replaced squeeze/optimal callee (ZopfliLZ77OptimalFixed / ZopfliLZ77Optimal),
   then tear it down with ZopfliCleanLZ77Store.  Those squeeze callees' contracts
